'''Ghanatɔ siwo le Germany''' nye Ghanavi dzidziwo kple dzidzime siwo ʋu yi alo le dɔ wɔm le [[Germany]]. Germany nye dukɔ evelia le [[Europa]] si me Ghanavi dzidzi nɔ gbeta wo ƒe xexleme sɔgbɔ le wu United Kingdom.<ref name="theafricancourier1">{{cite web|url=https://www.theafricancourier.de/features/ghanaians-in-germany-1950s-till-today/|title=Ghanaians in Germany – 1950s till today|date=2017-08-23|website=THE AFRICAN COURIER. Reporting Africa and its Diaspora!|language=en-US|access-date=2019-11-08}}</ref>

==Ŋtinya==
Kadodo nɔ Ghana kple Germany dome hafi Ghana xɔ ɖokuisi, egbe Amuga Ŋutome nɔ Germantɔwo ƒe kpɔkplɔte hafi xexeme ƒe aʋa gbãtɔ.<ref name="theafricancourier1"/>

== Ghanatɔwo ƒe Agbɔsɔsɔme ==
Ghanavi dzidzi siwo le Germany ƒe xexleme anɔ abe 40,000 lɔƒo. Ɖevi siwo dzidzi do tso Germany kple Ghana srɔɖelawo dome ƒe xexleme anɔ abe 9,729 tso ƒe 1965 va seɖe ƒe 2006 me. Le ƒe 2007 me la, 20,329 Ghanavi dzidziwoe xɔ agbǎle le seŋuti le Germany, wo ame 8,194 woe xɔ agbǎle eye wo vazu Germaniaviwo tso ƒe 1980 yi ƒe 2007.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.migration4development.org/sites/m4d.emakina-eu.net/files/The_Ghanaian_diaspora_in_Germany.pdf|title=The Ghanaian Diaspora in Germany|last=|first=|date=|website=|access-date=2019-11-16}}</ref>


